<h3 class="wp-block-heading has-large-font-size">Fieldwork</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"fontSize":"small"} -->
<p class="has-small-font-size">Fieldwork helps students immensely to tie in concepts most students may only read on paper to real-world scenarios and living, breathing people. That's why we intentionally and strategically take students into the community to connect classroom concepts with real-world applications.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"placeholder":"Content…","fontSize":"small"} -->
<p class="has-small-font-size">From museums to businesses, government institutions to green spaces, students gain practical experience navigating and contributing to the world around them. This deliberate approach transforms the city into an extension of our learning environment, making education more relevant, engaging, and impactful.</p>
